Replace Missing Numerical Values

Einstein Discovery allows you to replace missing numerical values in your model. Use the Replace Missing Variables transformation to enable statistical imputation on a numeric variable. 
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

In Model Setup, select a numeric variable that contains missing or null values.
Click the Transform dropdown menu and select Replace Missing Values.
Calculate the values by selecting average, median, or mode from the Replace with dropdown menu.
Select the variable that you want to derive imputed values from the For variable dropdown menu.
